\id RUT - Rohingya Bible
\h Rut
\toc3 RT
\toc2 Rut
\toc1 Rut
\mt1 Sĩyara Rut
\c 1
\s1 Ek gór manuš raṛor ṭaimot Muabot hãroigilgoi
\p 
\v 1 Još okkole šašon goribar agor ṭaimot dešot ek bar raṭ oil. Ar Ehudiyar Betlehemottu ekzon manuše, hitar bou edde dui futore fũwati loi Muab dešot hãroigilgoi.
\v 2 Manušwar nam aššilde Elimelek, hitar bouwor nam aššilde Naumi, ar hitar dui futor nam aššilde Mahlon edde Kilion. Itara aššilde Ehudiyar Betlehemor Efrat-guštir manuš. Itara Muab dešot giye edde heṛe roiye.
\p 
\v 3 Bade Naumir šuwami Elimelek mori gilgoi, henot hiba hibar dui futore loi roiye.
\v 4 Bade hitara duizone dui Muabi hoinniare biya goijje: ekzonor nam aššil Orpa, ar ekzonor nam aššil Rut. Hitara onumanik doš bosor heṛe bošoti goijje.
\v 5 Tarfore Mahlon edde Kilion, hitara dunizono mori giyegoi, ar Naumi šuwami hara, fuwain hara, duni mikkattu eka oi roiye.
\s1 Naumi edde hibar futor bouwain
\p 
\v 6 Bade Naumi hibar futor bouwain dunizon fũwati loi Muab dešottu firi zaiboilla uṭṭil; haron hibaye Muab dešot fuinnil ze \nd Mabude\nd* hibar mainšor uwore nozor diye edde ahar der.
\v 7 Hiyanor zoriya hiba zeṛe takito he zagttu niyolle, ar fũwati hibar dui futor bouwain o aššil, Toi hitara Ehudiya dešot uwafes firi zaiboilla fõt bai baisa diye.
\p 
\v 8 Hetunot Naumiye hibar dui futor bouwaindore hodde: "Tũwara tũwarar mar górot firizogoi. Mora okkololla edde ãlla ze raham goijjio, Mabud tũwarare o he bafe raham gorok.
\v 9 Tũwara dunizone zene šuwamir górot bissram fo, Mabud tũwarare hendilla dula dok." Toi hibaye hitarare suma diye; henot hitara guzori handa šuru goijje.
\v 10 Ar hibare hodde: "Na, ãra o tũwar fũwati tũwar zatir heṛe firi zaiyum."
\p 
\v 11 Kintu Naumiye hodde: "Oh ãr hoinnia okkol, firizogoi, tũwara ãr fũwati kiyolla zaiba? Tũwarar šuwami oi farefan ãr feṛot ki aro morod fuwa oibar aša ase?
\v 12 Oh ãr hoinnia okkol, firizogoi; haron ãr boyoš oiye, ãi abar biya gori no faijjum. Ar zodi o aša ase hoi aijja raitta biya gori, ar futain zormo di.
\v 13 Toile tũwara ki hitara zuwan ofan ofekka gori tai fariba? Hitaralla ki tũwara biya no gori boi taiba? No no, Oh ãr hoinnia okkol! Iyan tũwarattuwaro ãttu aro beši titar lager, kiyollahoile \nd Mabudor\nd* hãt ãr berudde giye!
\p 
\v 14 Henot hitara abar guzori handa šuru goijje. Toi Orpaye hibar horire sumadi bidai loiye, kintu Rute hibar hórire ãzamari dori taigiyegoi.
\v 15 Tehon Naumi hodde: "Sa, tor zal hibar mainšor edde hibar devotar hãse firigiyegoi, tui o tor zalor fise fise firizagoi."
\p 
\v 16 Kintu Rute hodde: "Tũware felaizaite, tũwar fisa lowattu firizaibolla ãre no hoiyo: Kiyollahoile
\q1 zeṛe tũi zor, ãi o zaiyum,
\q2 ar zeṛe tũi takor, ãi o takiyum.
\q1 Tũwar zati, ãr zati,
\q2 ar tũwar Allah, ãr Allah.
\q1 
\v 17 Zeṛe tũi moror, ãi o morium,
\q2 edde heṛe ãre hobor diya ok.
\q1 Moron sara ar kissuye zodi ãre edde tũware zuda gori fare,
\q2 toile Mabud ãre beši gozob dok!"
\m 
\v 18 Naumi zehon dekilo hibar fũwati zaibolla Rut mon sokto gori ereda gorifelaye, tehon hibaye hibare ar kissu no hoilo.
\p 
\v 19 Bade hitara dunizon zaite zaite Betlehem zehon fõssiyegoi, farar agagura hitarar babute howa hoi šuru oiye; mayafuwain okkole hodde: "Iba Naumi no?"
\v 20 Hibaye hitarare hodde: "Ãre Naumi (zara mani kuši) no ḍaikkio, bolke Mara (zar mani tita) ḍako, Kiyollahoile Šorbo-šoktiwalaye ãr zibonore beši tita gori diye.
\v 21 Ãi hár kissu furon gori loi baisa dilam, kintu ehon Mabude ãre hali hat loi firai ainnye. Tũwara ãre Naumi hoi ka ḍakor zehon \nd Mabud\nd* ãr bifokkede forman diye, ar Šorbo-šoktiwalaye ãre hoštot felaiye.
\p 
\v 22 Ei bafe Naumi firi aišše, hibar fũwati hibar futor bou Rut o, ze Muab dešottu firi aišše. Toi hitara Betlehem aiššede šomot gĩu da šuru oiye.
\c 2
\s1 Rut loi Buazor deha
\p 
\v 1 Naumir šuwami Elimelekor guštir ekzon ijjotdar tuwangor egena aššil; tãir nam Buaz.
\v 2 Ek dinna Muabiya Rute Naumire hodde: Ãi ketor kuṛat zaiore ze ãre rahamotor nozore giudanar sóra feṛaito de, tar fise fise giudanar sóra feṛaigoi. Naumi hoil: Okena, za oh zi.
\v 3 Bade hiba zaiore ek ketor kuṛat fošol haṛoya okkolor fise fise kuṛat foijjia giudanar sóra okkol feṛailowa šuru goijjil. Ar endilla oilo, ze kuṛat Rute giudana feṛail hiyan Elimelekor egena Buazor ket.
\v 4 Ar so, Buaz Betlehemottu aišše edde fošol haṛoya okkolore hoil: Mabud tũwarar fũwati takok. Tara zuwabe hoil: Mabud õnore o duwa gorok.
\v 5 Bade Buaz fošol haṛoya okkolor uwore zimmadarore fusar goijjil, Iba haro zobuti? hoi.
\v 6 Tehon zimmadare hoil: Iba Muabiya zobuti, ze Naumir fũwati Muab dešottu aišše.
\v 7 Hibaye ãttu fusargoijjil, meherbanigori fošol haṛoya okkolor fise fise zai kuṛattu giudanar sóra feṛai loifaijjum ne hoi. Hiba binna loti ehon foijjonto eṛe ase; bana ekkenagori góror butore aiššil edde zirail.
\b
\p 
\v 8 Toi Buaz Rutore hoil: Fun; oh ãr maya fuwa, tui giudana feṛaito oinno ketot no zais, ei ketottu no zaisgoi, ãr zobuti bandi okkolor fũwati eṛe tak.
\v 9 Fošol haṛoya okkol zeṛe fošol haṛibo hikka diyan raki tui bandi okkolor fise fise zais. Tor gat hat no defan ãi zobuk okkolore hoidir. Ar fanir tirašlagile tui oi górar hãse zai, zobuk okkole ze fani tuli raikke henttu fihaisgoi.
\v 10 Henot hibaye meṛit sojida fori tare salam gori hoil: Ãi boideši, õne ãre eto faṭṭa dor, õnor sarme ãi ei doya kiyottu failamde?
\p 
\v 11 Buaze zuwab dil: "Tor šuwami mori bade tui tor horire zendilla goijjios edde nizor ma bab, zormostan sari ek osin zatir hãse aiššos, he šob hota beggun ãi fuinni.
\v 12 \nd Mabude\nd* tore, tui zin goijjos hinor enam dok; He Israilor Allah, \nd Mabudor\nd* fakor nise zehon tui assoro loito aiššos, hibaye tore furafuri bafe enam dok."
\p 
\v 13 Hibaye Buazore hoil: "Oh ãr malik, õne ãre rahamotor nozore so; õnor ei bandire šantona dila edde šantir hota hoila, zodi o ãi õnor bandi okkolor laikka no."
\p 
\v 14 Tarfore hána háibar ṭaim zẽtte oil Buaze hibare hoil: Tui eṛe ai ruṭi hagai, tor ruṭir ṭukura rošot burai lo. Bade hibaye fošol haṛoya okkolor ḍakottu boiššil, ar Buaze hibare baijja dana dil. Toi hibaye feṭbori hána háil. bade aro hodun basitaigilgoi.
\v 15 Bade hiba giudana feṛaito zehon uṛil, Buaz tar mainšore hokum dil: Hibare dolagoijjattu feṛailoito do, edde hibare hũnki no diba hoi.
\v 16 Oh, tũwara hodun giudanar tarattu ṭani hiballa raki do, zene hiba feṛailoi fare, ar honokiye hibare dõk no diba.
\p 
\v 17 Ar hibaye hazinna foijjonto he ketot giudana feṛail. Bade hibar feṛaiya giudana hinore baijjaiore onumanik ek ari foijjonto giudana oil.
\v 18 Bade hibaye hin tuliloi šohorot uwafes firigilgoi. Horiye hibar feṛaiya giudanar bosta dekil; ar Rute basitakkilde he hánagun o hibar fũwati loiannil, ar hinore hibar horir munttu niyolaidil.
\v 19 Tehon horiye hibare hoil: Tui aijjia hoṛe feṛaios? Hoṛe ham goijjos? Ze tor mikka rahamotor nozor diye, Allah tare rahamot gorok. Tehon hibaye har hãse ham goijje, hin horire zanail. Hibaye endilla hoil: Ze manušwar hãse aijjia ãi ham goijji tar nam Buaz.
\v 20 Henot Naumi hibar futor boure hoil: Tare rahamot gorok he Mabude ze doya deha bondogori no fele zinda edde mora okkolor uwore. Naumi aro hoil: Hite ãrar egena, ãrare dehašuna goribar zimma asede tarar butorottu ekzon.
\v 21 Ar Muabiya Rute hoil: Te ãre endilla o hoiye, ãr šomosto fošol daiya šeš no o foijjonto tui ãr mainšor fũwati fũwati takis.
\v 22 Tehon Naumi hibar futor boure hoil: Mare, oinno honokiyor ketot, tore honokiye zalafura gori no farefan, tar hamor mayafuwaindor fũwati fũwati takon tolla bala oibo.
\v 23 Toi fošol daiya šeš no o foijjonto, hibaye giudana feṛaibolla Buazor hamor mayafuwaindor fũwati fũwati takil edde hibar horir fũwati bošobaš goijil.
\c 3
\ms1 Buazor hõlat Rut
\p 
\v 1 Ek din Naumiye Rutore hodde: Oh zi! Ãi tolla ki ekkan gór sešta no goijjum zene tui šuk fos?
\v 2 Fun! Tui ze Buazor bandi okkolor fũwati aššili, hite ki ãrar egena no ne? Sa, hite aziya raitta hõlat giudana uraibo
\v 3 Tui ga du edde kušbo tel bebargor, ar tor šundoijjia hoor findi oi hõlat za, kintu tar há fiya šeš no o foijjonto tui tare tor foriso no dis.
\v 4 Te zẽtte neiṭṭo zaibo, tehon tui tar bisana otgori rakibi. Bade heṛe zaiore tui tar saddorgan ṭengor uwottu atorgorifelai heṛe neṛizaibigoi. Ar ki goraforibo hin te tore hoibo.
\v 5 Hibaye zuwabe hoil: Tũi zen hor, hin beggun ãi goijjum.
\p 
\v 6 Bade hiba oi hõlat lamigil edde hibar horiye zendilla hokum dil, he mozin hibaye beggun goijjil.
\v 7 Buaz há fiya gorifelail edde tar mondil kuši oil, te giudana ṭalor hãsat zai neiṭṭilgoi. Ar Rut aste aste zai tar ṭengor uwottu saddorgan algaifelail edde heṛe neiṭṭil.
\v 8 Bade ada raittot maze Buaz somkiuṛiṭṭil edde faš bodolil. Ar so, ekzon beṛimanuš tar ṭengor ḍake neṛitaikke.
\v 9 Toi hite fusar goijjil: Tui hon? Hibaye zuwabdil: Ãi tũwar bandi Rut. Tũi tũwar saddoror tole bandire assoro do, haron tũi ãr dehašuna goroya egenar buttotu ekzon.
\v 10 Te hodde: Allar rahamot ok tor uwore, oh zi! Ei foijjonto tui ze fakka dilolade hiyan dehaiyos ehon hinottu aro beši fakka dilolade hiyan dehaili. Kiyollahoile tui tuwangor otóba gorib hono ḍoilla zobukor fise no zos.
\v 11 Ehon tui, oh zi, ar no ḍorais. Tui zã hoibi ãi tolla hin beggun goijjium. Haron tui ze beši bala maya fuwa hiyan ãr farar manuš beggune zane.
\v 12 Ar ãi tor dehašuna goroya egenar buttotu ekzon hiyan soiyi, kintu ãttu aro hãsor ar ekzon egena ase.
\v 13 Tui aijjia raittia eṛe tak. Binna zodi te tor dehašunar bar lo, toile hite hen gorok, ar zodi hite tor dehašunar bar no lo, toile zinda Mabudor hosom gori hoir, ãi tor dehašunar bar loiyum; binna no o foijjonto tui eṛe neṛitak.
\p 
\v 14 Tarfore Rut binna fozor o foijjonto tar ṭengor ḍake neṛitakkil, edde ekzone ekzonore sini no farede hendilla andar takite hiba neṛattu uṛigilgoi, haron Buaze hibare hoil: Hõlat ze ekzon maya fuwa aišše hiyan honokiye no zana foribo.
\v 15 Te aro hoil: Tor gar šallan loi ikka ai edde hiyanore tor munttu gori dor. Ar hibaye šallanore munttu gori doril, toi te so barang giudana mafi hibar matar uwore tulidil. Toibade hite šohoror uzu gilgoi.
\p 
\v 16 Bade Rut zehon hibar horir hãse aigilgoi, hibaye fusargoijjil: Ken ken oil, oh zi? Henot hibaye beggun kulasagori hoil, Buaze hibare zen zen goijje.
\v 17 Hibaye horire aro hoil: Te ãre horir hãse halihate no zais hoi ei giudana so barang in ãre diye.
\v 18 Ei hota funi Naumi hoil: Tui sofor gor, oh zi, šeše hondilla o sasena! Aijjia iyanore hono šabišto no oite te no tamibo.
\c 4
\s1 Buaz loi Rutor biya
\p 
\v 1 Bade Buaz ṭaun-geiṛot zai heṛe boiššilgoi. Ar so, ze dehašuna goroya egenar hota Buaze hoil te hehon henttu aiššil. Buaze tare, Oh, folona omuk hoi ḍakdil edde hoil: "Eṛe aio, boiyogai." Toi te fottottu ai boššilgai.
\v 2 Bade Buaze došzon bura murubbi okkolore ḍaki hoil: Onora eṛe boio. Toi tara o aiyore boššilgai.
\v 3 Buaze he dehašuna goroya egena hitare hodde: Naumi Muab dešottu firi aišše, hibaye ãrar egena Elimelekor zobingan besito sar.
\v 4 Hetolla ãi bafilam ei befargan tũwarare zanaon dorhar. Eṛe zara aišše tarar sarme edde ãr zatir bura murubbi okkolor sarme tũi hiyan kinilo. Tũi zodi zobingan surailoito so, toile surailoifelo. Ar zodi tũi no loito so toile ãre ho, haron hiyan surailoibar odihar beggunor age tũwar, ar tũi bade ãr. Tarbade he dehašuna goroya egenaye hodde: Ṭik ase, ãi hiyan surailoium.
\v 5 Henot Buaze hoil: Tũi ze din he zobingan Naumir hãsottu kiniloiba, hedin tũwattu Rut, he Muabiya rarire o gosaforibo, zene mora manušwar odihare, tar nam edde tar zobinor mirazdar take.
\v 6 Ei hota funi oi dehašuna goroya egenaye hodde: Ãi henoile hiyan surailoi no faijjum, hen goillye ãr nizor fuwaindor miraz nošto gorifelayifan oibo. Ãr zagat tũi surailo, haron ãi surailoi nofarir.
\p 
\v 7 Surailowa edde besa-kina in okkol age Israil dešot endilla rosom aššil ze hota fakka goribolla ekzonor ṭengor zuta ar ekzonore dito, ei bafe boni-Israil hono hamor goba goitto.
\v 8 Toi oi dehašuna goroya egena hite Buazore: Hiyan tũi kinilogoi, hoi te tar ṭengor zuta kulidil.
\v 9 Tehon Buaze bura murubbi edde heṛe aiššilde tara beggunore hoil: Ãi Naumir hãsottu Elimelek, Kilion edde Mahlonor šomosto šombotti kiniloilam, aijjia tũwara hinor goba oila.
\v 10 Zene morar nam tar afon báiyaindor edde farattu buzi no zagoi, edde he šombottittu mirazdar okkole miraz fa, ar he mora manušwar odihare tar nam uddar goribolla ãi ãr bou hisabe Muabiya hoinnia Rut, Mahlonor boure kobul gorilam. Tũwara aijjia ei šomostor goba oila.
\v 11 Toi heṛe ṭaun-geiṛor butore zara boiššil, tara šoho bura murubbi okkole hoil: Oi, ãra goba oilam. Ze maya fuwa tũwar górot aiyer hibare Mabude Rahela edde Leyar ḍoilla gora ok, zarar duwara šomosto boni-Israil lami aišše. Ar Eferatot tũwar kamiyaf ok edde Betlehemot tũwar nam mošur ok.
\v 12 Mabud he zobutir feṛottu ze fuwain tũware dibo, tarar butottu di tũwar bongšo zen Tamaror feṛot Ehudar fuwa Ferošor bongšor ḍoilla o.
\s1 Rutor futi oilde badša Daud
\p 
\v 13 Bade Buaz Rutore biyagoril edde Rut tar bou oil. Buaz hibar hãse gil, toi Mabud Rutor feṛot fuwa dil edde hibattu ekzon morod fuwa oil.
\v 14 Bade mayafuwain okkole Naumire hoil: Allare šukuriya, Tãi aizo tũware dehašuna goroya egenattu siri nofele. Ei fuwar nam boni-Israilor maze mošur ok.
\v 15 Ite tũwar foranore abar tottoza gori tulibo edde tũwar bura boyošot tũwar deha šuna goribo, haron tũwar futor boue tũware adorgore, hibaye biyayede fuwa, ze tũwalla hãt futottu aro barik.
\v 16 Bade Naumi gura morod fuwaware kulot loil edde tare lalon falon gora šuru goijjil.
\v 17 Bade Naumiye ekzon morod fuwa faiye! En hoi ḍen gór bam górjjiya okkole tar nam rakil. Tara tar nam rakkil Obed. Obed aššilde Yašir bab, Yašir aššilde Daudor bab.
\p 
\v 18 In oilde Ferošor hãndan okkolor nam: Ferošor fuwa Hešron,
\v 19 Hešronor fuwar nam Ram, edde Ramor fuwa Omminadab,
\v 20 Omminadabor fuwa Nahušon, Nahušonor fuwa Salmon,
\v 21 Salmonor fuwa Buaz, Buazor fuwa Obed,
\v 22 Obedor fuwa Yasir, Yasiror fuwa Daud.
